  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Prevenar Immunogenicity in High Risk Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>To Evaluate the Humoral Immune Response to a Conjugated Pneumococcus Vaccine 7-Valent (Prevenar®) in Children From High Risk Groups.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
